N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 28.1 - Sale

State Regulations

No holder of a distributor's alcohol permit shall sell or
agree to sell any alcohol to any person who is not duly licensed to purchase
and/or use alcohol at the time of such agreement and sale. Notes
